<item>
            <title>[LU-8499] wireshark plugins don&apos;t build any more</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8499</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch e14246641c04c9e3004043f58f469532223d06d6 added some code to the wireshark plugin to handle the new ladvise feature, but the changes appear to have broken the wireshark build. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On a side note, would it be possible to add a wireshark compile to the jenkins build so that there is coverage?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
